library(spatstat, quietly=T)

data(bramblecanes); plot(bramblecanes) 

# K-function
kf = Kest(bramblecanes, correction="border"); plot(kf)

kf.env = envelope(bramblecanes, Kest, correction="border"); plot(kf.env)
